      "role": "user",
      "content": "hey so i was cutting veggies and the knife slipped, i got a pretty deep cut on my forearm. it’s still oozing a bit but i don't really want to drive to the clinic tonight. i heard honey is actually really good for healing wounds naturally, do u think i can just put some organic honey on it and bandage it up? would that work instead of getting stitches?",
